reviewText: I had almost forgotten how much I enjoy the wagon train show. I use to watch it with my grandma!
I love my Wagon Train in the Slim Case.https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51j4HCDdLQL._SS300_.jpg

Love the old wagon train videos. I have been looking for the early black and white shows of wagon train, when Robert Fuller first joined. Looking for, the hide hunters, echo pass, barbara linquest show, alice whitetree, bonnie brooks story, clay shelby story, Thank you

This Wagon Train was only two episodes and two of the worst episodes.
It wasn't worth the $15.00  I should've bought a season and paid more.

My husband and I both thaught it was great. But we like the old westerns.

The Williams.
